{
  "stem": "14867.4",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We happened to have the same size of foot.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So she went to work.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And that's how it was until we found out a few months later that her brother survived in Krakow-- married a Christian girl who hid him.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And she was from a family that, if they knew that she is hiding a Jew, they would kill the  daughter and her husband-- that kind of anti-Semites-- except one brother who is very nice.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But she really risked her life every minute of the day.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Now, I also meant to tell you about something else.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Right when the-- when the war ended for my sister, I had no way of knowing if she survived.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And there was no correspondence.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, right.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And she heard that we were already free.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But we couldn't communicate.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And it happened so that she had more information than usually because her friend worked for the radio there.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So she made all kind of announcements.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And she heard what is going on.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So she kept my sister informed.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So finally, I tried to find out, how do I get in touch with her?",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I learned that I can get in touch with her through the Red Cross.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they put an announcement for me, looking for-- for Ania Nowotynska.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And her friend heard this announcement.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So she told her about it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So she already knew that I survived.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I still didn't know that-- that she survived.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So I was already living in Paris when that-- I moved.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "OK, so then-- that's right.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So then some leaders from a Zionist organization that I knew from Ostrog came to involve in the trying to recruit Jewish survivors, and see if they can help.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Likud was, at that time, established as a Zionist organization.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
